44:48.929 --> 44:50.887
and we need your voice,

44:50.970 --> 44:53.136
we need your prayers,

44:53.220 --> 44:55.637
because Satan walks
outside that door...

44:57.136 --> 45:00.303
...that beast who tempts us

45:00.387 --> 45:03.136
and teases us

45:03.220 --> 45:05.220
and pulls us

45:05.303 --> 45:08.595
down, down,

45:08.679 --> 45:12.345
down to the everlasting pit

45:12.428 --> 45:14.804
where the crown of thorns

45:14.887 --> 45:16.804
rips at our skin.

45:18.220 --> 45:21.470
We must fight him.

45:21.553 --> 45:25.095
We must stand up
and be heard!

45:25.178 --> 45:29.679
We can no longer
be weak and powerless.

45:29.762 --> 45:32.011
Women, do you hear me?

45:32.095 --> 45:33.345
Yes.

45:33.428 --> 45:35.887
