to your friends, the Nazis,

50:45.095 --> 50:46.470
right here in LA,

50:46.553 --> 50:48.637
probably the same ones
that murdered your friend.

50:48.720 --> 50:50.387
You stupid fucking putz!

50:53.053 --> 50:55.637
Now, Mr. Schiff, he's a--
he's a good Jew,

50:55.720 --> 50:56.637
you understand.

50:56.720 --> 50:58.762
